HEADWORD: Masora
<hw>Ma*so"ra</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NHeb.
<ets>m⟦amac⟧s⟦omac⟧r⟦amac⟧h</ets> tradition.]</ety> <def>A Jewish
